#### 5. Seating Layout Preview
**Impact:** High | Type: UX/Visualization

**Implementation:**
- Visual grid representation of hall seating
- Row labels: A-Z (dynamic based on hall rows)
- Column numbers: 1-n (dynamic based on hall columns)
- Seat type indicators:
  - O = Regular (blue)
  - V = VIP (yellow/gold)
  - W = Wheelchair (light blue)
- Color-coded seat tiles with hover tooltips
- Screen indicator at top for orientation
- Legend explaining seat symbols

**Business Value:**
- Training tool for new staff
- Customer inquiry support
- Visual verification of seating configuration
- Accessibility planning and compliance visualization

**Files Modified:**
- `models/Hall.js`:
  - Added `generateSeatingLayout()` instance method
  - Algorithm distributes seat types across rows/columns
  - Returns structured array: rows → seats → {type, label, position}
  - Added private helper `_getSeatLabel()` for symbol mapping
- `services/hallService.js`:
  - Enhanced `getHallStatistics()` to include seatingLayout in response
- `controllers/hallController.js`:
  - Added `show()` method to display hall details page
  - Passes seating layout data to view
- `routes/hallRoutes.js`:
  - Added `GET /:id` route for hall details (placed before /:id/edit to avoid conflict)
- `views/halls/show.ejs`: **NEW FILE**
  - Complete hall details page
  - Statistics cards for capacity, screenings, status
  - Seat type distribution with progress bars
  - Seating layout grid visualization
  - Custom CSS for seat styling
  - Hall information table
- `views/halls/index.ejs`:
  - Added "View Details" button (eye icon) to action column

**Visualization Algorithm:**
```javascript
// In models/Hall.js
hallSchema.methods.generateSeatingLayout = function () {
    const layout = [];
    let seatIndex = 0;
    
    // Create seat type map based on distribution
    const seatMap = [];
    if (this.seatTypes && this.seatTypes.length > 0) {
        this.seatTypes.forEach(seatType => {
            for (let i = 0; i < seatType.count; i++) {
                seatMap.push(seatType.type);
            }
        });
    }
    
    // Fill remaining seats with regular
    while (seatMap.length < this.capacity) {
        seatMap.push('regular');
    }
    
    // Generate rows (A, B, C, ...)
    for (let row = 0; row < this.rows; row++) {
        const rowLabel = String.fromCharCode(65 + row); // A, B, C, etc.
        const seats = [];
        
        for (let col = 0; col < this.columns; col++) {
            const seatType = seatMap[seatIndex] || 'regular';
            seats.push({
                row: rowLabel,
                column: col + 1,
                type: seatType,
                label: this._getSeatLabel(seatType)
            });
            seatIndex++;
        }
        
        layout.push({ rowLabel, seats });
    }
    
    return layout;
};
```

