### Performance Considerations

**Positive Impacts:**
- Virtual properties computed on-demand (no storage overhead)
- Seating layout generated only when viewing details (not on list page)
- Maintenance conflict query uses indexed startTime field
- Seat distribution calculated in O(n) time where n = seat types (typically ≤ 3)

**Optimization Opportunities:**
- Consider caching seating layout if halls frequently viewed
- Add compound index on (hall, startTime) for faster conflict detection
- Lazy load seating layout grid if halls exceed 20 rows

**Scalability:**
- Current implementation supports up to 26 rows × 50 columns = 1,300 seats
- Seating layout generation scales linearly with capacity
- No N+1 query issues introduced

